Description:
    Installs SignupGuard into a Rails app.

    Generates a config initializer, copies the gem's migrations into your
    db/migrate, and adds a requires_review boolean to your User model.

Examples:
    bin/rails generate signup_guard:install
    bin/rails generate signup_guard:install --user-class=Account
    bin/rails generate signup_guard:install --skip-user-migration
    bin/rails generate signup_guard:install --skip-stimulus
    bin/rails generate signup_guard:install --requires-review-attribute=needs_review
    bin/rails generate signup_guard:install --stimulus-path=app/javascript/src/controllers/signup_timer_controller.js
